    "long_instructions": "## Generating Content Chat\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to generate content you could actually use in your product launch.\r\n\r\nFocus on content that connect to your assigned role (e.g., name + slogan, visuals, script, or jingle).\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n1. Use AI Chat to turn your best idea from brainstorming into real content.\r\n    - What do you want AI to help you write or describe?\r\n    - What should it sound or feel like?\r\n    - What should it include?\r\n2. In your Activity Guide under Stage 3: Generating Content, write:\r\n\t- The question or prompt you gave to AI\r\n\t- A summary of what the AI told you\r\n3. Want better results? Use specific language in your prompt—like the tone you want, key phrases to include, or the audience you’re trying to reach.",
